N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2509.4 - Confidentiality

State Regulations

Registration pursuant to this Part shall not be subject
to the Freedom of Information Law, provided that registration information
relative to a tenant, owner, lessor or subtenant shall be made available to
such party or his authorized representative. Notes
